    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It\u2019s in such incredible shape, it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car from day one\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel because it\u2019s basically perfect! Come check it out!",
      "price": 43500.0,
