    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, showcasing a flawless exterior with a deep-gloss finish, free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. The interior is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history and an engine bay so clean it reflects its pampered life. From the crystal-clear lenses to the untouched alloy wheels, this car represents the pinnacle of its model. For the discerning buyer seeking perfection, this is an unparalleled opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 43900.0,
