      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mated to a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been fully overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced with Turner plates for structural longevity. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling via refreshed bushings and OE dampers. Draped in flawless Carbon Black Metallic over Cinnamon Nappa leather, this vehicle displays zero parasitic draw or fluid seepage. A true collector-spec icon with a linear power band and a perfectly functioning M-Variable limited-slip differential.",
